channel.title: View Private Myspace Profiles
channel.description:
Well, I don't need to see the profile to see it. There is a custody battle over a child at the moment and there are some pictures and comments that I would like to get off of the profile. I've tried URL tricks and javascript injections but of course none of it worked. So I would like to know how I could view images of the profile.
(The Profile is private and she will not add anyone new, and using one of her friends profiles is not an option)
